title: Water tomato plants
description: Check drip irrigation system and water tomato plants in North Field A. Monitor soil moisture levels.

title: Harvest lettuce
description: Harvest mature romaine lettuce from South Field B. Cut in early morning for best quality.

title: Apply fertilizer to corn
description: Side-dress corn plants with nitrogen fertilizer. Apply 50 lbs per acre.

title: Weed carrot beds
description: Hand weed carrot beds in West Field 2. Be careful not to damage carrot tops.

title: Prune apple trees
description: Winter pruning of apple trees in Orchard Block C. Remove dead, diseased, and crossing branches.

title: Soil preparation
description: Prepare soil for spring planting in empty field sections.
